title: Millions Of Youtubers Are My First Love

description:
Description :
        Millions of YouTubers Are My First Love, YouTuber at manhua websiteI once missed the chance to stand on the stage with you, this time I want to muster up the courage to challenge it again!" Yi Yao, a woman who always silently lights up other people's achievements, mustered up the courage to participate in the channel management competition of "Exploration Team No. 11", a group to which Xu Ping belongs, to recruit partners, in order to have the opportunity to shoot with her high school first love, Xu Ping, who is also a millionaire YouTuber. "0% no, 1%, I'll bet with you on this 1% possibility." After Tang Xuelin, her best friend in the past who has a soft heart, decided to assist Yi Yao in the recruitment, the channel that had not made any progress had explosive growth. However, in the face of the fiercely competitive and cruel YouTube circle, all kinds of unimaginable difficult challenges will test Yi Yao one by oneRecommend for you !
